            Dag 179
            <span>Roadtrip down south</span>
        </h1>
        <time datetime="2015-02-13">13. februar 2015 . Addo, Chintsa, J-Bay og Mossel Bay, Sør-Afrika</time>
        <img class="main-image" src="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8576/16171296734_26953992b6_k.jpg" alt="" />
